153
00:08:55,820 --> 00:08:56,530
he will definitely

154
00:08:56,650 --> 00:08:57,980
kill every one of us here.

155
00:08:59,890 --> 00:09:00,730
Your Highness.

156
00:09:04,100 --> 00:09:05,650
This is enough.

157
00:09:06,420 --> 00:09:07,980
Today, Tianqi City

158
00:09:08,650 --> 00:09:09,420
