191
00:11:08,130 --> 00:11:09,060
Consort Xuan?

192
00:11:09,420 --> 00:11:09,980
Yes.

193
00:11:10,580 --> 00:11:11,770
I am pretty sure that Tianqi City

194
00:11:12,250 --> 00:11:12,850
