228
00:12:19,300 --> 00:12:21,250
Whether the news is real or fake,

229
00:12:21,530 --> 00:12:23,010
the people of Tianqi City

230
00:12:23,940 --> 00:12:25,730
already believe it to be true.

231
00:12:27,980 --> 00:12:28,580
